{"tid":870532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國驚驚　冀港媒勿成干擾中國政治基地　中宣部部長訓示報道離奇消失","createTime":"2018-10-21T07:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T08:41:46.000Z","uid":47714,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5aafd9599228bc761a74b315a00b14b1f321d45","tid":870532,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-16-2018/48731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-16-2018%2F48731&d=BqY1nZ9xAMQx3w6LkQeDmDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ddc99691\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-16-2018/48731</a><br />\n<br />\n香港傳媒高層訪京團代表，今日與中宣部部長黃坤明會面，到傍晚時份，訪京團代表、星島集團行政總裁蕭世和會面後向傳媒表示，黃坤明希望香港媒體不要成為「干擾內地的政治基地」，之後多個媒體都有報道相關言論。<br />\n<br />\n然而，曾經在報道中引述「干擾內地論」的媒體，相關報道連結到晚上不是變成「死Link」，就是把該段新聞轉成另一總點。多個主流媒體，在報道中亦未見提及「干擾內地論」。<br />\n<br />\n據《東網》及《蘋果》報道指，有中聯辦官員稱「干擾內地論」屬內部言論，不作公開。"},{"pid":"7469c7f886faa03676750c53d0bba57067867b70","tid":870532,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩制呢？"},{"pid":"945be8d531b09085d37ea9f69c20709a43befc16","tid":870532,"uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"香港干擾大陸政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港豬何德何能<br />\n<br />\n你唔干擾我地已經偷笑啦"},{"pid":"f7c88fb583ddbb43af6987f267e429fec78f1ad9","tid":870532,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7469c7f886faa03676750c53d0bba57067867b70","tid":870532,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩制呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:11:27.000Z","msg":"仲兩制？<br />\n等2047俾中國消滅？<br />\n而且宜家中國都消滅緊你"},{"pid":"23feb424bb48d0ac51eeab180017ccaa5868ec5d","tid":870532,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"945be8d531b09085d37ea9f69c20709a43befc16","tid":870532,"uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"香港干擾大陸政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港豬何德何能<br />\n<br />\n你唔干擾我地已經偷笑啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180915002883-260409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180915002883-260409&d=BqY1nZ9xAMQx3w6LkQeDmDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=83896c31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180915002883-260409</a><br />\n<br />\n呢單新聞其實同呢單新聞聯動<br />\n真實動機唔係話有人干預支那<br />\n而係同白區黨/匪諜知開始要對外敵對<br />\n拉起封鎖線"}]}